                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

[2021-01-21 10:14:32] => 14.102.45.21  =>   =>  SELECT  (
                      SELECT COUNT(*)
                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id = 1 AND l.lead_status_id = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      LEFT JOIN quote_product qp ON qp.quote_id = q.quote_id
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = q.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = qp.product_item_id
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM proforma_invoice pro_inv 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = pro_inv.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN proforma_invoice_product pip ON pip.proforma_invoice_id = pro_inv.proforma_invoice_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pri ON pri.product_item_id = pip.product_item_id
                      WHERE pro_inv.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(pro_inv.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM buyer_order o 
                      LEFT JOIN leads l ON l.lead_id = o.lead_id
                      LEFT JOIN buyer_order_product op ON op.buyer_order_id = o.buyer_order_id
                      LEFT JOIN product_items pi ON pi.product_item_id = op.product_item_id
                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS order_count

                      FROM   leads l WHERE l.status !=2 AND l.lead_type_id != 1 AND l.lead_status_id != 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS lead_count,
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM leads l 
                      WHERE l.status = 3   AND STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(l.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS opportunity_count,
                      
                      (
                      SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quote q 
                      WHERE q.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(q.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
                      ) AS quotation_count,
                      
                      (

                      ) AS proforma_invoice_count,

                      WHERE o.status != 2   AND STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') >= STR_TO_DATE('2021-04-01', '%Y-%m-%d') and STR_TO_DATE(o.created_on, '%Y-%m-%d') <= STR_TO_DATE('2022-03-31', '%Y-%m-%d')
